perf list: Add usage

Currently 'perf list' is not very helpful if you forget the syntax:

  $ perf list -h

  List of pre-defined events (to be used in -e):

After:
  $ perf list -h

   usage: perf list [hw|sw|cache|tracepoint|pmu|event_glob]

